high_descs: Move forward, then right and face the bed on your right.
Take the lap top from the bed in front of you.
Turn right and face the brown desk in front of you.
Place the lap top on the brown desk in front of you.
Turn around and face the bed in front of you.
Close the lap top on top of the bed in front of you and take it.
Turn around and face the brown desk in front of you.
Place the lap top on the desk in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place lap tops on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right at the television,  turn right to face the foot of the bed.
Put the top of the lap top down, pick up the lap top from the bed.
Turn right and walk to the desk across the room.
Put the lap top on the desk to the left of the CD.
Turn and walk back over to the bed.
Close the lap top and pick it up from the bed.
Turn around and walk back over to the desk.
Put the lap top on top of the CD on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two lap tops to the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around to face the left side of the table.
Pick up the lap top on the table.
turn right and walk across the room to face the desk.
Place the lap top on the desk.
Turn around and walk forward to face the side of the bed.
Pick up the lap top on the back of the bed.
Turn around and walk forward to face the desk.
Place the lap top next to the first lap top on the table.
anns.task_desc: To move two lap tops to the desk.
